</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r1" x="0" y="166.4" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-6)">│</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r5" x="231.8" y="166.4" textLength="732" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-6)">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Run&#160;`aws&#160;configure`&#160;or&#160;`aws&#160;configure&#160;sso`&#160;and&#160;relaunch.</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r1" x="1451.8" y="166.4" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-6)">│</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r3" x="1464" y="166.4" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-6)">
</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r1" x="0" y="190.8" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-7)">│</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r5" x="231.8" y="190.8" textLength="646.6" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-7)">&#160;&#160;-&#160;Credentials&#160;are&#160;valid&#160;but&#160;the&#160;IAM&#160;principal&#160;lacks</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r1" x="1451.8" y="190.8" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-7)">│</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r3" x="1464" y="190.8" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-7)">
</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r1" x="0" y="215.2" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-8)">│</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r5" x="231.8" y="215.2" textLength="719.8" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-8)">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;`s3:ListAllMyBuckets`&#160;(root&#160;listing)&#160;or&#160;`s3:ListBucket`</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r1" x="1451.8" y="215.2" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-8)">│</text><text class="terminal-2156439797-r3" x="1464" y="215.2" textLength="12.2" clip-path="url(#terminal-2156439797-line-8)">
